name: FNF - Vs. Annie Full Week
description:
A mod that replaces WEEK 3 with silly little songs and character.

Features 4 Original Songs:
GOOD ENOUGH

LOVER

TUG OF WAR
and ANIMAL that replaces Winter Horrorland.

* The only difference between the difficulties is the speed at which the arrows scroll up. The charts themselves are exactly the same.

This mod only replaces assets related to Week 3 and Week 5 for the most part.
